  "texts": [
    "ConclusionsAn efficient human motion intention prediction mechanism was implemented in the current research work using deep learning techniques and multimodal data.",
    "In the first phase, EEG/EMG signals were used as input and converted into spectrogram images.",
    "Then, these images were given to the AH-CNN-LSTM-based motion intention prediction region.",
    "Here, the IYSGA technique was utilized to tune the LSTM and CNN model parametersto maximize the MCC and reduce the FDR to attain an accurate human motion intention prediction outcome.",
